Title: Launch Party (2)
Plot: In this hour long special, its the launch of the new Dunder Mifflin Infinity website and Michael is anticipating going to the launch party in NYC. At the Scranton branch, Angela and the Party Planning Committee plan a satellite party. Meanwhile, Dwight competes against the website to be top seller of paper in a day.
GuestStars: Kevin McHale, Dan Cole, Brad Graiff, Nick Armstrong, Scott Damian
